name: Disable Woo Analytics
author: Print Science

sections.description:
The default WooCommerce analytics may not be useful to you. The calculations for the default reports can slow your site and server down. This simple plugin removes the Analytics items from the left menu in the admin pages.

Arbitrary section
sections.installation:
This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.

  1. Install the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
sections.faq:
Does the Designer plugin require WooCommerce

Yes. You must have WooCommerce installed.
